Recent Developments

In April 2024, Amcor Plc, in collaboration with Kimberly Clark, introduced a new packaging bag for its Eco Protect diapers, incorporating 30% recycled materials. These bags are crafted from post-consumer recycled content, providing a more sustainable packaging solution for hypoallergenic diapers made from certified plant-based fibers
In January 2024, ProAmpac unveiled ProActive Intelligence Moisture Protect (MP-1000), a new product designed to manage moisture levels in packaging solutions
In May 2023, DuPont completed the acquisition of Spectrum Plastics Group, a company specializing in the manufacture of specialty medical devices and components
